
Downloaded Avro-tools-1.8.1.jar file

avro-tools-1.8.1.jar 

Created avro schema file(log.avsc)

with the help of avro-tools-1.8.1.jar converted json to avro(log.avro) using the below command,

java -jar avro-tools-1.8.1.jar fromjson --schema-file log.avsc /home/mani/Logs/logs1.json > /home/mani/Logs/log.avro

